{"tid":2232209,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"用地塞米松 疑病況嚴重","createTime":"2020-10-06T08:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T08:53:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a64f9de95d4c4b36e56ed904a87541d6a723837","tid":2232209,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:38:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201006/4AIBZB3S4VCLZN6MNOF4ULGVM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201006%2F4AIBZB3S4VCLZN6MNOF4ULGVM4%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKK0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=50630b20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201006%2F4AIBZB3S4VCLZN6MNOF4ULGVM4%2F&h=790b83f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201006/4AIBZB3S4VCLZN6MNOF4ULGVM4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n用地塞米松 疑病況嚴重<br />\n<br />\n白宮醫療團隊為總統特朗普處方重症病人才使用的類固醇「地塞米松」（dexamethasone），令人質疑他的病情可能很嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n英國的試驗發現，血氧含量低和需要接受氧氣治療的病人使用地塞米松後，存活機會增加、住院日數亦減少，對須依賴呼吸機的病人效用更大。倫敦帝國學院實驗醫學教授奧彭肖表示，地塞米松通常用於出現徵狀一周或以上、呼吸系統有問題的病人身上，很少處方予發病時間相對短的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6D4HxtJ7FQ5s0Tow36M_XcGDG10=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7LSRTQXQD5GBRJPN6KRAB6VPQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6D4HxtJ7FQ5s0Tow36M_XcGDG10%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7LSRTQXQD5GBRJPN6KRAB6VPQM.jpg&h=4d441d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■主診醫生康利被質疑淡化總統病情。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚少用於初病者<br />\n<br />\n美國傳染病學會也指，地塞米松對需要額外氧氣的重症者有效，同時有研究發現它對輕症病人沒有幫助，甚至損害他們的健康。而很多醫生都認為，讓在病症初期的病人使用抗病毒藥物「瑞德西韋」是較合理的做法，意味地塞米松可能只會在沒有更好選擇的情況下才處方給病人。<br />\n<br />\n美國伯靈頓雷希醫院暨醫學中心傳染病專家麥奎林表示，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》/路透社"},{"pid":"f722d647bf5b1912c10fb09cb7a0ec8483c15210","tid":2232209,"uid":49747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:50:11.000Z","msg":"嚴重到出左院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce717cad033e66d0f4d1ce5082c282d3c130e8b","tid":2232209,"uid":254165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:53:53.000Z","msg":"總統唔用最勁嘅藥唔通死先用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}